  "detailed_description": "<h1>What do others say?</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/342cf1718298c92a8a0ac1fcc062f8bd.avif?t=1733252492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras_big/342cf1718298c92a8a0ac1fcc062f8bd.avif?t=1733252492 width=800 height=456 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/bcff037c5b2ddd6bba65e35064daebdf.avif?t=1733252492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras_big/bcff037c5b2ddd6bba65e35064daebdf.avif?t=1733252492 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bread</strong> is not your average clicker game — it’s a carb-loaded journey of endless bread-clicking madness! The rules are simple: click on a loaf of bread. That’s it. But don’t be fooled by the simplicity! Every click is a step toward bread-clicking greatness. Will you become the ultimate Bread Master, or will your fingers cramp up in the pursuit of glory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock hilarious achievements like “<strong>First Slice</strong>” or “<strong>Baking Bread</strong>” and discover the thrill of clicking your way to fame. Think you can handle the ultimate challenge of “<strong>Timeless Bread Clicker</strong>”? 100,000,000 clicks stand between you and eternal bread-clicking legend status!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no baking involved — just pure, unadulterated bread-clicking action. Ready to click your way to the top? Grab your loaf and let the clicking begin!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/2a5137c9474535921679c7429d4ac762.avif?t=1733252492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras_big/2a5137c9474535921679c7429d4ac762.avif?t=1733252492 width=800 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/32b2f5377922923bc20bb8c6c05d5ac6.avif?t=1733252492\" width=763 height=496 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/bcff037c5b2ddd6bba65e35064daebdf.avif?t=1733252492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras_big/bcff037c5b2ddd6bba65e35064daebdf.avif?t=1733252492 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bread</strong> is not your average clicker game — it’s a carb-loaded journey of endless bread-clicking madness! The rules are simple: click on a loaf of bread. That’s it. But don’t be fooled by the simplicity! Every click is a step toward bread-clicking greatness. Will you become the ultimate Bread Master, or will your fingers cramp up in the pursuit of glory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock hilarious achievements like “<strong>First Slice</strong>” or “<strong>Baking Bread</strong>” and discover the thrill of clicking your way to fame. Think you can handle the ultimate challenge of “<strong>Timeless Bread Clicker</strong>”? 100,000,000 clicks stand between you and eternal bread-clicking legend status!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no baking involved — just pure, unadulterated bread-clicking action. Ready to click your way to the top? Grab your loaf and let the clicking begin!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/2a5137c9474535921679c7429d4ac762.avif?t=1733252492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras_big/2a5137c9474535921679c7429d4ac762.avif?t=1733252492 width=800 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249680/extras/32b2f5377922923bc20bb8c6c05d5ac6.avif?t=1733252492\" width=763 height=496 />